tpl-test
========

tpl-test is the test module for testing libtpl-egl frontend APIs


GBS Build Instruction
---------------------

- Build libtpl-egl:
  $ gbs build -A armv7l

- Build libtpl-egl with tpl-test:
  Change the value of 'ENABLE_TPL_TEST' from 0 to 1 in libtpl-egl.spec
  Then, build like below

  $ gbs build -A armv7l --include-all


Run Tests
---------

- Run
  $ cd /opt/usr/tpl-test
  $ ./tpl-test


- Run with configuration
  $ ./tpl-test --config.width=720 --config.height=1280 --config.depth=24

